    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 assessment plan. Quantitative validation demonstrates NIH prediction error of 8.3% MAPE, well within the 15% acceptance threshold. Relative hemolysis index RH = 0.87 satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion at worst-case operating conditions. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
